   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC4c1a16a82b2310058d68a5fdf30dcfc4"></a>Removal of the fuel tank flange
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4519"> </a>Remove the panel (<a href="77975.html#DUCc08298b82a73100585b0e07f17a720d2">Removing the panel</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4524"> </a>Remove the seat (<a href="77991.html#DUC7dd8e1d82a971005810ccc3160c450d2">Removing the seat</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4529"> </a>Remove the front half-fairings (<a href="77983.html#DUC6b420cf82a8210058217e66c96b901d2">Removing the front half-fairing</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4534"> </a>Remove the tank fairings (<a href="77987.html#DUC104f7d582a9610058109cc3160c450d2">Removing the tank fairings</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4539"> </a>Remove the fuel tank (Removing the fuel tank<a href="79858.html#DUC4747a3202b2310058d67a5fdf30dcfc4"></a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4544"> </a>Loosen the six nuts (1) securing the fuel tank flange. To lift the flange, remove three screws, and leave the other three
            ones in a cross pattern.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4546"> </a>Remove the fuel pump (2) from the fuel tank.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_8_001403647.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4551"> </a>Recover the sealing washer (3).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4553"> </a>Undo and remove the two retaining screws (G) and move the protection (F).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4555"> </a>Loosen the two nuts (4) and remove the fuel filter (5), recovering the two O-rings (6).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4557"> </a>Before reassembly, carefully remove any deposits or scale from all parts.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/important.jpg">Important
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4560"> </a>When installing the new filter, position it so that the arrow stamped on the outer casing points towards the flange.
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/note.jpg">Note
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4563"> </a>The flange is supplied as a spare part complete with the fuel pump and pressure regulator: the entire flange assembly must
         be replaced in the event of malfunction.
      </div>
